room_title: Escape room "Chainsaw Bob" by QQuest Escape Games in Miami
room_address: 717 E Atlantic Blvd Pompano Beach, FL 33060
room_description: As the serial killer was leaning over you with a chainsaw, you instantly recognized him. The infamous Chainsaw Bob is known for his choice of weapon. Just a centimeter before it hit your face, the saw broke! Now Bob has to step out and get a new one. He'll be gone for an hour; can you escape your fate?
